Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.07,0:00:08.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not much has changed at Hogwarts since last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.17,0:00:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only Kim fell off the ladder
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:14.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,during her part-time job in Hrochoť
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.11,0:00:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and impaled her throat directly on the rake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During a difficult operation,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.80,0:00:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which lasted 260 hours
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.82,0:00:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they miraculously managed to eliminate her retardation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But her vocal cords will be damaged for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Ľudo Kolman,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.12,0:00:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,under the threat of extermination of all Jews
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.99,0:00:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,converted to Islam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Mr. Pipík was replaced by one distinguished professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.12,0:00:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A very interesting year at Hogwarts was awaiting for Dano Drevo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:00:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Štúdio POG presents:
