Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.17,0:02:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Miro Žbirka - 22 dní]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:26.97,jergus-gombit,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it is true that even shit looks better than you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:28.97,jergus-gombit,,0000,0000,0000,,but we'll figure something out about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.97,0:02:32.31,patkan,,0000,0000,0000,,Ancient Jewish medicine could help you -
