Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:35.54,patkan,,0000,0000,0000,,with vaginal discharge,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:37.87,patkan,,0000,0000,0000,,it doesn't look that bad at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:40.76,jergus-gombit,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Žbirka, don't worry, we'll figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:43.24,patkan,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it time and the skin will regenerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:45.04,jergus-gombit,,0000,0000,0000,,Time heals all wounds, Mr. Žbirka,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.04,0:02:46.48,jergus-gombit,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:49.27,zbirka,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm curious how will I in this shape (...) Slávik.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.54,0:02:50.88,jergus-gombit,,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't understand it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:53.63,jergus-gombit,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you fucking fall into a bath of acid in Patince?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:55.99,zbirka,,0000,0000,0000,,I just lost my balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:02:57.51,patkan,,0000,0000,0000,,But looks don't matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:02:58.73,patkan,,0000,0000,0000,,you still have gold in your throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.52,0:03:00.12,zbirka,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Patkaň!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.12,0:03:02.54,jergus-gombit,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Žbirka, I have a great idea:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:04.46,jergus-gombit,,0000,0000,0000,,yesterday I got so fucking wasted,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:05.38,jergus-gombit,,0000,0000,0000,,I puked over myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.17,0:03:06.38,zbirka,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerguš, to the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:07.34,jergus-gombit,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:09.34,jergus-gombit,,0000,0000,0000,,What if we did a tournament at Hogwarts?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:10.96,zbirka,,0000,0000,0000,,What tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:13.07,jergus-gombit,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious you need a new face
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:15.85,jergus-gombit,,0000,0000,0000,,well, and there are young and beautiful students at Hogwarts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.85,0:03:18.32,jergus-gombit,,0000,0000,0000,,You will organize a tournament under the guise of a big win
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:21.22,jergus-gombit,,0000,0000,0000,,and in the end you will take the face of the fittest handsome person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:23.22,jergus-gombit,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a vile and insidious plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:26.83,zbirka,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a bad idea at all, Jerguš.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:30.96,zbirka,,0000,0000,0000,,It would even solve my wart problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:34.92,zbirka,,0000,0000,0000,,And now invite the old man outside for coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:41.25,zbirka,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:42.65,zbirka,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather waste him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:49.56,kim,,0000,0000,0000,,Dano! Dano, get up! Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:51.00,kim,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, he shit himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.16,kim,,0000,0000,0000,,Dano! Get up.
