Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:21.18,peter-senior,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I'm so looking forward to the egg-throwing race.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.47,0:04:24.39,peter-senior,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we will meet Mr. Fekete and his son Šaňko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.39,0:04:26.62,peter-senior,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm warning you kids, they are Olaš Gypsies,
